{"id":430898,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/03/除了人日还有哪些其他党姓媒体心系日本女优/","date":"2016-03-04T09:10:19Z","modified":"2016-03-04T08:11:46Z","title":"除了《人日》，还有哪些其他党姓媒体心系日本女优？","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://freeweibo.com/weibo/3949094907060641\">@曹山石</a>：人民日报微信公众号今晚封面文章的配图，是女优青木麻奈。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/7c1d7ba8gw1f1k4dvj2xbj20k00zk77b.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430899\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430899\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/7c1d7ba8gw1f1k4dvj2xbj20k00zk77b.jpg\" alt=\"7c1d7ba8gw1f1k4dvj2xbj20k00zk77b\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/7c1d7ba8gw1f1k4dvj2xbj20k00zk77b.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/7c1d7ba8gw1f1k4dvj2xbj20k00zk77b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/7c1d7ba8gw1f1k4dvj2xbj20k00zk77b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n（曹山石原微博已被删除，以上内容来自<a href=\"http://freeweibo.com/\">自由微博</a>）</p>\n<p>青木麻奈原作画面：<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/21-1409151004380-L.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430900\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430900\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/21-1409151004380-L.jpg\" alt=\"21-1409151004380-L\" width=\"350\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/21-1409151004380-L.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/21-1409151004380-L-234x300.jpg 234w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n（图片来自网络）</p>\n<p><strong>2015年1月，新华社推特官方认证账号被曝光收藏了日本重口味色情图片：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>方舟子 ‏<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fangshimin/status/555175068414664704\">@fangshimin</a>：新华社的认证推特账号不知道是谁维护的，居然还收藏了日本硬核淫秽图片推特。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430904\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430904\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口1.jpg\" alt=\"新华社重口1\" width=\"500\" height=\"246\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口1.jpg 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口1-300x148.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>当月，又被美国《时代》杂志网站曝出新华社，<strong>一个中国国家通讯社，其官方推特账号关注了一个专发日本色情图片的账户</strong>：</p>\n<blockquote><p>《时代》原文标题：<a href=\"http://time.com/3688912/xinhua-japanese-porn-china-news-agency/\">Is China’s Official News Agency Following a Japanese Porn Feed on Twitter?</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口2-copy.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430906\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430906\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口2-copy.png\" alt=\"新华社重口2 copy\" width=\"400\" height=\"681\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口2-copy.png 617w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口2-copy-176x300.png 176w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/新华社重口2-copy-601x1024.png 601w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2011年，央视法制节目曾被曝为案件当事人女友配了中国人民的老朋友 苍井空 的照片：<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/ccav_苍井空.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-430901\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-430901\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/ccav_苍井空.png\" alt=\"ccav_苍井空\" width=\"350\" height=\"719\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/ccav_苍井空.png 860w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/ccav_苍井空-146x300.png 146w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/ccav_苍井空-768x1577.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/03/ccav_苍井空-499x1024.png 499w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n（<a href=\"http://news.163.com/11/0715/09/790AJ97K00011229.html\">网易新闻截图</a>）</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[11813,12025,9807,18804,19844,22609,23589,10702,19125]}